title: India’s NSE Targets IPO in Seven to Eight Months, CNBC Says
description: The National Stock Exchange of India Ltd. plans to launch its initial public offering in the next seven to eight months, CNBC-TV18 reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Ashish Kumar Chauhan.
